ntly then &quot;Hey, wanna camp orc 2 with me?  It's good XP!&quot;), I think he refuses to let an issue drop, and expects far too much from the server populace as a whole.  If he wants the non-stop, intense level of Roleplay, with no one participating to a lesser degree, he should turn off the computer, and put together a pen &amp; paper group.<br><br>   I'm not sorry he left.  I don't mean that to sound rude, I just don't think that his leaving was anyone's &quot;fault&quot;.  He's been distraught for what, months now?  Hopefully wherever he does go, be it another server, or off of EQ in general, he'll find the gameplay he's looking for and it'll make him happy.<br><br>- Syll <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top">  Page  <b>1</b> <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm4.showMessageRange?topicID=292.topic&start=21&stop=40>2</a><a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm4.showMessageRange?topicID=292.topic&start=41&stop=60>3</a><a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm4.showMessageRange?topicID=292.topic&start=61&stop=75>4</a> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm4.showMessage?topicID=302.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm4.showMessage?topicID=301.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm4.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=292.topic&index=20><img src=http://www.firiona-vie.com/images/arfv.jpg border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"><a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm4.threadControl?topicID=292.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/professional/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator only)</a><br> <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm4.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=292.topic>S